<document>
	<header>
		<title>Related projects</title>
	</header>
	<body>
		<p><strong>HiveMind</strong> is a services and configuration microkernel:</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong><link href="http://tapestry.apache.org">Tapestry</link></strong>: Web framework
				  that uses HiveMind under the covers.
			</li>
			<li><strong><link href="http://hivetranse.sourceforge.net/">HiveMind Utilities</link></strong>: Repository of HiveMind extensions
				for the support of transaction handling, security, remoting, events and rich clients.
			</li>
			<li><strong><link href="http://crispy.sourceforge.net/">Crispy</link></strong>: Client for Remote Invocation for different kinds of services via proxies.
				Offers an extension for the invocation of HiveMind services.
				
			</li>
			<li><strong><link href="http://mule.codehaus.org/">Mule</link></strong>: Enterprise Service Bus (ESB) messaging framework
				that supports HiveMind as object container.
			</li>
			
		</ul>
	</body>
</document>
